extends layout

block content
  #commands
    h1 Play songs through voice commands
    p
      | This demo uses speech recognition and the 
      a(href='https://developer.spotify.com/web-api/') Spotify Web API
      |  to play songs. Try it using some of the commands below. Remember to allow the use of the microphone.
    p For instance "Play Some Nights"
    h2 Voice commands
    ul
      li Play {song name}
      li Play {song name} by {artist name}
  #conversation
footer
  | This demo uses the Spotify Web API and the library 
  a(href='https://github.com/TalAter/annyang') annyang
  |  to make it easy to match recognised text with rules.
